<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Yangon [Rangoon], June 23 (XINHUA) -- Myanmar 
[Burma] leader Senior General Than Shwe said here today that the 
visit of the Chinese military delegation to Myanmar will not 
only strengthen the understanding and friendship between the two 
armies but also contribute to the development of cooperation 
and relation between Myanmar and China. 
  At the invitation of Myanmar Ministry of Defense, the 
Chinese 
goodwill military delegation of the People's Liberation Army 
