Council (SLORC) and commander-in-chief of defense services, 
than Shwe also said that he hopes that the exchange of the 
visits and the cooperation between the two countries and the two 
armies will further strengthen the friendly relationship, 
established by old leaders of the two countries, must be kept on 
generation by generation. 

