about the set-up of their organizations and how they manage 
their business. 
  During its stay in NZ [New Zealand], the delegation headed 
by 
Li, also minister of the State Commission for Restructuring the 
Economic Systems, had extensive contacts with NZ officials and 
business people to exchange views on the reforms in China and 
New Zealand. 

