<H3> <TI>   Sino-Foreign Arbitration Agreements Signed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Sino-Foreign Arbitration Agreements Signed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2306124894 Beijing XINHUA in English 1234 GMT 23 Jun 94 </F>
