------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Fruit                    |1.5375 million tonnes    |31.2                     | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 


  Forestry production progressed. The province planted 956,500 
mu of land, attained great achievements in the "357" project, 
and covered all barren hills with green trees. Fujian tops the 
nation in afforestation, winning the title of "advanced province 
in afforesting barren hills." 
  Animal husbandry developed steadily, and output of meat, 
poultry, eggs, milk, and animal by-products increased. 


------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
|Output of Animal By-Products, Numbers                                        | 
------------------------------------------------------------------------------- 
